# CJK allowlist for the no-cjk CI gate.
#
# cyntex is English-only: the gate rejects any CJK character (Chinese/Japanese/
# Korean ideographs, CJK punctuation, full-width / half-width forms) in tracked
# files. This file is the ONLY escape hatch.
#
# Each non-comment line is a git pathspec (relative to the repo root) that is
# excluded from the scan. Examples (do not enable without review):
#   some/module/src/test/resources/fixtures/cjk-sample.json
#   */messages_zh.properties
#
# It ships EMPTY on purpose. No directory — tests, data fixtures, or locale
# resource bundles included — is exempt by default. Adding a path here is a
# reviewed decision.
